<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 04 at 6:28AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>....Reduced Visibility This Morning Due to Fog....
Fog will continue to reduce visibility into this morning with
visibility at only one to two miles with patchy areas as low as a
quarter mile. Motorists are encouraged to allow extra travel time
and reduce speed during the morning commute. Keep in mind that
visibility may change over short distances leading to even more
challenging travel conditions.</description>
